name: Math Toolbox
body:
### The Calculator of the Future!
This is a new Java Application by ThexXTURBOXx (Nico).
It calculates things like quadratic equations, Pythagoras, etc.
Support for simple Physics and Chemistry is planned.

### Authors and Contributors
ThexXTURBOXx alone:
 - 16 years old
 - German
 - 11th grade, will study Computer Science and Maths (maybe as teaching profession)

### Support or Contact
Just create a [new Issue here]().
If you already know how to fix it, then create a [new Pull Request here]().
If you just want to translate this to another language, then follow the instructions in the [README]().
